beagle: beagle (Beagle Desktop Search Tool)
beagle: 
beagle: Beagle is a search tool that ransacks your personal information space to 
beagle: find whatever you're looking for.  More technically, Beagle is a Linux 
beagle: desktop-independent service which transparently and unobtrusively indexes 
beagle: your data in real-time.
